:<font size="15">רכב</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
רכב / rekeb / reh'-keb

===Etymology===
From {{HH|7392}}; 

===Noun===
'''רכב'''

# A vehicle; by implication a team; by extension cavalry; by analogy a rider, that is, the upper millstone: - chariot, (upper) millstone, multitude [from the margin], wagon.

